WEBVTT

00:02:29.798 --> 00:02:33.120
because I was so excited about what I'd found,

00:02:33.120 --> 00:02:35.424
but I was just about to graduate from college

00:02:35.424 --> 00:02:37.200
with a degree in political science,

00:02:37.200 --> 00:02:39.734
and I'd always had this dream

00:02:39.734 --> 00:02:41.960
of going to Washington, D.C.,

00:02:41.960 --> 00:02:44.202
and sitting at a desk

00:02:44.202 --> 00:02:46.920
and working in government.

00:02:46.920 --> 00:02:48.968
(Laughter)

00:02:48.968 --> 00:02:52.168
Why did this have to get in the way of all that?

00:02:52.168 --> 00:02:53.746
I made the tough decision

00:02:53.746 --> 00:02:57.158
of going home after graduation

00:02:57.158 --> 00:03:00.258
and not going up to Capitol Hill,